This is a retrofit demo with a jSonPlaceholder
    https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/

We are learning how to get the Get request

(1) Add the dependency for retrofit.
    -> go to google and search for retrofit square
    https://square.github.io/retrofit/

(2) use kotlin serialization plugin
    -> id 'org.jetbrains.kotlin.plugin.serialization' version '1.5.31'
           implementation "com.jakewharton.retrofit:retrofit2-kotlinx-serialization-converter:0.8.0"
           implementation "org.jetbrains.kotlinx:kotlinx-serialization-json:1.3.0"

(3) add json dependency to parse the data.
    (you can find this on the same retrofit page)

(4) create a data class with the json converter plugin.
    -> copy and paste the json output

(5) do the gradle setup for koin
    ->